  "title": "Workplace Safety and Health Officer",
  "description": "<p><u>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct daily onsite inspection ensure compliance to safety rules, Environment, Health and Safety regulation and customer requirements.</li>\n  <li>Assist with the management for investigating and identifying causes of accident and determining measures to prevent occurrences.</li>\n  <li>Attend safety walks and inspections before or during each project to analyze safety risks.</li>\n  <li>Investigate accidents that occur onsite and identify possible causes of the accident.</li>\n  <li>Maintain documentation of the company’s safety procedures, accidents and related events.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with relevant ISO and safety audit. (Eg, ISO, ConSASS &amp; GGBS)</li>\n  <li>Other duties that may assigned by the company.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u>Job Requirements</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of working experience in the related field.</li>\n  <li>Candidates to possess Certificate in workplace safety and health.</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Resulted oriented, independent and self-motivated.</li>\n</ul>",
